114
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:19,720
Here, Ms. Ning,

115
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:21,520
let’s change seats.

116
00:07:33,650 --> 00:07:37,190
First of all, the Ning family

117
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:40,550
