122
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,930
It showed his great sincerity.

123
00:07:57,030 --> 00:07:59,200
Let's toast to Mr. Su.

124
00:08:17,350 --> 00:08:17,790
Eat.

125
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:42,159
I'm sorry,

126
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,580
