127
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:47,670
I'm sorry,

128
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:50,060
please excuse me for a moment as well.

129
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,050
Why are you here?

130
00:09:03,190 --> 00:09:05,270
I saw how cold Su Yu was treating you,

131
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,620
and I couldn’t stand it.

132
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:10,230
Right now,

133
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:13,610
aren't I the only one who can help you?

134
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,480
Come out.

135
00:10:07,430 --> 00:10:07,960
Mr. Ning,

136
00:10:08,950 --> 00:10:10,810
I would like to give a toast to you.

137
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:17,280
We are a family now,

138
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,700
