139
00:10:21,010 --> 00:10:21,810
Uncle Ning.

140
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:24,960
Don't you think "Uncle Ning" sounds a bit distant?

141
00:10:30,590 --> 00:10:31,550
You

142
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,110
should call me Dad.

143
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,690
I guess you still need to get used to it.

144
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:52,830
Dad,

145
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:57,040
Su Yu and I will toast to you together.

146
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:10,270
Sit.

147
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:13,990
Xi,

148
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:15,940
let us toast to your sister.

149
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:16,830
Come on.

150
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:25,190
Mochen,

151
00:11:25,410 --> 00:11:26,730
Xi and I toast to you.

152
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:29,110
We wish you and Su Yu a happy engagement.

153
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:41,700
Ms. Ning has such a high alcohol tolerance.

154
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,700
Let me propose a toast to you as well.

155
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,080
Well,

156
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:11,310
