163
00:12:25,810 --> 00:12:27,810
I think we should take it slow first.

164
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,970
That's true.

165
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,920
You guys have your own plans,

166
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:32,800
I won't interfere anymore.

167
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:34,870
However, there's one thing I need to let you guys know.

168
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:37,530
No matter how the relationship is between you two,

169
00:12:37,530 --> 00:12:39,990
don't let it affect the company's business.

170
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,060
Of course.

171
00:12:41,570 --> 00:12:43,040
