174
00:12:47,070 --> 00:12:48,730
please excuse me for a moment.

175
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:02,430
I'm sorry,

176
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:04,290
please excuse me for a moment.

177
00:13:48,070 --> 00:13:48,910
Bai Li.

178
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:51,950
You know who I am?

179
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:53,570
Of course I do.

180
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:54,750
Bai Li,

181
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:56,510
are you feeling lost

182
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,090
from sleeping for so long?

183
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,590
