186
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:30,390
Su...

187
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:39,520
What?

188
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,810
What are you afraid of?

189
00:14:44,570 --> 00:14:46,490
You will never get rid of me.

190
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,800
Never.

191
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:51,350
Never!

192
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:53,180
What's wrong?

193
00:14:56,390 --> 00:14:57,150
My phone.

194
00:14:57,150 --> 00:14:57,890
Don't move.

195
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:10,050
Where am I?

196
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:12,530
