199
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,170
You're allergic to mushrooms.

200
00:15:19,890 --> 00:15:21,060
Mushrooms?

201
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,190
Don't you know

202
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,160
