206
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:34,390
Did you bring me here?

207
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,210
This is the test report.

208
00:15:41,740 --> 00:15:43,100
If you don't need anything,

209
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:44,230
I'll be leaving now.

210
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:50,270
Why did you save me?

211
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,420
Don't think too much,

212
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:53,850
I just followed my instincts.

213
00:15:53,850 --> 00:15:55,040
As a human...

214
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:00,600
Ning Mochen?

215
00:16:01,310 --> 00:16:02,040
Ning Mochen?

216
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:08,370
