220
00:16:25,210 --> 00:16:30,040
♫Then you're the irreplaceable cure♫

221
00:16:27,350 --> 00:16:28,550
Thank you,

222
00:16:28,910 --> 00:16:30,190
Su Yu.

223
00:16:32,580 --> 00:16:37,400
♫You're the only one I care about in this crowded city♫

224
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:45,020
♫I'm determined to have my heartbeat get closer to yours♫

225
00:16:47,410 --> 00:16:50,710
♫You say love is like♫

226
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:50,830
Professor,

227
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:54,370
♫A rainstorm that wind can't blow away♫

228
00:16:51,350 --> 00:16:52,350
I'm sorry,

229
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,680
