230
00:16:55,350 --> 00:17:00,140
♫No matter how it hysterically♫

231
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,390
You prepared so long

232
00:16:59,990 --> 00:17:01,310
for this design competition,

233
00:17:01,110 --> 00:17:05,660
♫Calls out someone's name♫

234
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:03,270
