235
00:17:03,910 --> 00:17:04,589
Bai Li,

236
00:17:05,619 --> 00:17:06,630
I'm not going anywhere.

237
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:07,670
I'm going to stay and take care of you.

238
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:12,210
