Her dad is waiting,

284
00:18:59,150 --> 00:19:00,350
we'll be leaving now.

285
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:36,750
Su Yu.

286
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:41,710
You’re awake.

287
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,450
Don't move.

288
00:19:51,950 --> 00:19:53,010
Your fever is gone.

289
00:19:54,950 --> 00:19:58,390
You stayed here with me the whole night?

290
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,420
Don't think too much,

291
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:03,300
I would do the same for a stranger.

292
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:06,670
But don't you hate me?

293
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,040
I'm not you,

294
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:12,080
I won't hurt someone just because I hate them.

295
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:15,510
Then yesterday, during dinner,

296
00:20:16,030 --> 00:20:18,900
when you saw Ye Yunkai touch me like that,

297
00:20:19,230 --> 00:20:20,590
why didn't you do anything?

298
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:21,860
Why should I care?

299
00:20:22,850 --> 00:20:24,200
Haven't you always been like this with him?

300
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:25,970
But you could tell that I didn't like it.

301
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:28,830
How would I know that you weren't just acting again?

302
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:38,070
Get up.

303
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:41,390
Slowly.

304
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:54,520
I asked someone to make this soup for you.

305
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:56,070
It got delivered here not too long ago,

306
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:57,130
so it's still warm.

307
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:06,410
Here.

308
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:11,400
Don't worry, it's not poisoned.

309
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:21,970
Why are you suddenly so nice to me?

310
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:25,820
Aren't you afraid that I'm just acting sick?

311
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,680
There's something I need to thank you for.

312
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,790
You helped me out yesterday

313
00:21:30,790 --> 00:21:32,550
when I was giving a toast.

314
00:21:35,700 --> 00:21:36,350
Oh.

315
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:51,990
Mr. Su, you're here, too.

316
00:21:52,010 --> 00:21:53,340
What are you doing here?

317
00:21:54,150 --> 00:21:55,210
I'm here to see you.

318
00:21:56,170 --> 00:21:58,230
I brought you your favorite flowers.

319
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:15,630
Mr. Su is taking care of you himself,

320
00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:17,990
I envy you.

321
00:22:18,430 --> 00:22:19,590
Is there something you want?

322
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:20,990
If not, you can leave.

323
00:22:21,150 --> 00:22:22,880
Look at the way you're talking,

324
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:24,510
I'm hurt.

325
00:22:29,570 --> 00:22:32,120
I noticed lately that you come to the hospital often.

326
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:34,120
I guess you're luck isn't that good.

327
00:22:38,490 --> 00:22:39,690
Are you here to see me?

328
00:22:39,710 --> 00:22:41,440
I’m mainly here to see Ms. Ning,

329
00:22:41,750 --> 00:22:44,010
but also to talk about business with you.

330
00:22:46,870 --> 00:22:48,000
Let’s talk outside.

331
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:56,710
Mr. Su,

332
00:22:57,190 --> 00:22:59,070
I’ve arranged the production line,

333
00:22:59,070 --> 00:23:01,260
when can I see your draft and sample?

334
00:23:01,280 --> 00:23:02,490
The draft is done,

335
00:23:02,520 --> 00:23:04,090
and the sample is in the making.

336
00:23:04,090 --> 00:23:07,490
When will you sign the contract for Bai Li's guardian rights?

337
00:23:08,050 --> 00:23:09,370
Don’t rush, Mr. Su.

338
00:23:09,890 --> 00:23:11,970
We just started working together

339
00:23:11,990 --> 00:23:13,590
and things are going so well.

340
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:15,500
It'll be great

341
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:17,600
if we can continue working together

342
00:23:17,840 --> 00:23:19,120
for a long time.

343
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,800
Ye Yunkai, what do you mean?

344
00:23:21,870 --> 00:23:23,200
Didn't we agree

345
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:24,720
that I'll sign your contract,

346
00:23:24,720 --> 00:23:25,620
and you'll sign mine?

347
00:23:25,620 --> 00:23:26,820
Don't worry,

348
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,900
I'm someone who always keeps my word.

349
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:31,600
But don't forget,

350
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:35,670
Bai Li is still my wife.

351
00:23:35,870 --> 00:23:37,530
I have to take good care of her.

352
00:23:39,730 --> 00:23:40,840
Scum.

353
00:23:40,970 --> 00:23:50,150
[Nurse in charge Xue Mengmeng]

354
00:23:40,970 --> 00:23:50,150
[Doctor in charge Su Chen]

355
00:23:47,030 --> 00:23:49,390
Mr. Su, I won't get mad at you.

356
00:23:54,170 --> 00:23:56,350
You should go keep your fiancée's company.

357
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:57,310
I'm leaving.

358
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:59,250
I'll be waiting for your good news.

359
00:23:58,050 --> 00:24:02,120
[Ruikang Hospital]

360
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:16,990
What did Ye Yunkai say to you?

361
00:24:20,630 --> 00:24:21,390
Su Yu,

362
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:25,320
you said you partnered with Ye Yunkai for profit,

363
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:28,870
then why did you give up the intellectual property right for free?

364
00:24:28,870 --> 00:24:30,600
This has nothing to do with you.

365
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,460
Why did you do that?

366
00:24:34,700 --> 00:24:35,580
Unless,

367
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:38,320
you're not doing this for money.

368
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:42,910
People die for money, birds die for food.

369
00:24:42,910 --> 00:24:44,840
Why would I do this if not for money?

370
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:48,800
Really?

371
00:24:52,770 --> 00:24:54,710
The doctor said you can be discharged at anytime.

372
00:24:54,710 --> 00:24:55,640
I'm leaving now.

373
00:24:56,990 --> 00:24:58,590
Remember to finish the soup.

374
00:25:06,690 --> 00:25:11,430
[Ruikang Hospital]

375
00:25:21,970 --> 00:25:23,930
There must be something

376
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:27,700
between Su Yu and Ye Yunkai that I don't know about.

377
00:25:49,070 --> 00:25:49,960
Song Yu,

378
00:25:51,250 --> 00:25:52,320
what are you doing?

379
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:54,900
Boss,

380
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:57,150
did you stay up all night?

381
00:25:57,270 --> 00:26:00,070
I want to finish these samples as soon as possible.

382
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:06,030
The design style of these products

383
00:26:06,550 --> 00:26:08,360
are very similar to your early projects.

384
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:11,050
Something about it feels different though.

385
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:14,360
What's different?

386
00:26:15,570 --> 00:26:17,800
I think there's an extra hint of softness.

387
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:19,940
It perfectly balances out

388
00:26:20,590 --> 00:26:22,070
with your early designs.

389
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:26,540
These works

390
00:26:27,230 --> 00:26:30,680
are very memorable to me.

391
00:26:31,370 --> 00:26:32,880
I can't believe such a perfect work

392
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:35,450
will be collaborating with a low-end brand like Chenyun.

393
00:26:35,450 --> 00:26:38,010
That Ye Yunkai looks like a New Money,

394
00:26:38,050 --> 00:26:39,580
he knows nothing about art.

395
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:43,080
I'm heading out.

396
00:26:49,670 --> 00:26:50,270
Mr. Ye,

397
00:26:50,750 --> 00:26:52,570
following your request, the Purchase Department

398
00:26:52,570 --> 00:26:54,430
has purchased enough materials.

399
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,750
The production line is also ready.

400
00:26:56,990 --> 00:26:59,750
As long as S&YU provides the drafts and samples,

401
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:01,930
we can start production immediately.

402
00:27:02,810 --> 00:27:04,220
But, Mr. Ye,

403
00:27:05,000 --> 00:27:07,350
since we greatly expanded our production line,

404
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:09,700
and stored up on many materials,

405
00:27:10,230 --> 00:27:12,670
our funds are quite tight.

406
00:27:13,250 --> 00:27:14,890
Will there be any problems?

407
00:27:15,740 --> 00:27:17,340
What problem could there be?

408
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:20,870
In my opinion, the scale isn't even big enough yet.

409
00:27:20,950 --> 00:27:23,110
I already applied for a loan and it'll be approved soon,

410
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,510
so be ready to receive it.

411
00:27:24,630 --> 00:27:25,270
But...

412
00:27:25,270 --> 00:27:26,110
But what?

413
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,550
Have you seen the preorder data?

414
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:32,720
There are so many consumers who are willing to buy it.

415
00:27:33,780 --> 00:27:36,580
This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for us.

416
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,030
If we succeed,

417
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:40,320
we will not only make a fortune,

418
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:42,430
but can also become a top brand.

419
00:27:45,530 --> 00:27:49,190
[S&YU Jewelry Design Corporation]

420
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:52,790
Ms. Ning,

421
00:27:53,790 --> 00:27:55,430
are you looking for Mr. Su?

422
00:27:55,750 --> 00:27:56,150
Yes.

423
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:58,340
Unfortunately, he just left.

424
00:27:58,860 --> 00:28:00,760
Mr. Su worked till late hours last night.

425
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,020
He's working too hard.

426
00:28:05,620 --> 00:28:06,980
This is?

427
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,340
Ms. Ning, look,

428
00:28:09,070 --> 00:28:10,800
this is Mr. Su’s latest design.

429
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:13,750
It’s similar to his early design styles,

430
00:28:13,750 --> 00:28:14,970
yet completely different at the same time.

431
00:28:14,970 --> 00:28:18,300
There seems to be an extra touch of a soft and feminine style.

432
00:28:21,050 --> 00:28:24,030
Is this Su Yu's draft

433
00:28:24,150 --> 00:28:26,100
for the collaboration with Chenyun?

434
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:26,710
Yes.

435
00:28:29,570 --> 00:28:31,330
But this is my design draft.
